ing: 1 (4 ounce) can pineapple chunks in juice
des: "Pineapple chunks, bananas, and real coconut milk give these a sweet, tropical flavor!"
ins: Place the pineapple chunks with juice, banana, coconut milk, and vanilla extract into a blender; puree until smooth. Pour into 6 ice pop molds and freeze until solid, about 4 to 5 hours.
